FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776636668
OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,F"The majority of Android phones we've
OL,7,Ftested in the last four years can be
OL,8,Feasily unlocked using a 2D image, and
OL,9,Fsome manufacturers are still failing
OL,10,Fto adequately warn their users that
OL,11,Fthis is the case.
OL,13,F"We'd urge affected users to set up
OL,14,Falternative methods of security, like
OL,15,Fa fingerprint or a PIN, which are much
OL,16,Fmore secure."
