OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,FWhich? Approached the companies
OL,7,Finvolved for comment.
OL,9,FA Fairphone spokesperson said: "At
OL,10,FFairphone, privacy and security are
OL,11,Ffundamental to our design.
OL,13,F"The Fairphone (Gen 6) utilises 2D
OL,14,Ffacial recognition, which is
OL,15,Fcategorised as a Class 1 biometric
OL,16,Funder Android's security framework.
OL,18,F"This is a widely adopted industry
OL,19,Fstandard utilised by many leading
OL,20,Fsmartphone brands and inherently
OL,21,Fshares the same limitations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
