PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776636668
OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,F"Because it is a Class 1 biometric,
OL,7,Fthe Android system automatically
OL,8,Fenforces strict security restrictions;
OL,9,FFace Unlock can only be used to access
OL,10,Fthe lock screen and is strictly
OL,11,Fblocked from sensitive actions, such
OL,12,Fas NFC payments or banking apps."
OL,14,FHonor told Which? that 2D systems have
OL,15,Ftechnical limits that can make them
OL,16,Fsusceptible to being tricked.
OL,18,FBecause of this, the feature should be
OL,19,Fused as a tool for convenience rather
OL,20,Fthan for authorising sensitive
OL,21,Ftransactions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
