OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,FUsers are informed during setup that
OL,7,Fthe system is less secure than a
OL,8,Fpassword, and for those needed top-
OL,9,Ftier security for banking Honor
OL,10,Fsuggests its pro models with 3D facial
OL,11,Frecognition.
OL,13,FMotorola said: "Security has always
OL,14,Fbeen at the core of what we do and the
OL,15,Fsecurity of our consumers remains a
OL,16,Ftop priority for Motorola.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
