OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,F"The Face Unlock technology is
OL,7,Fintended to support convenient
OL,8,Funlocking of the phone, although
OL,9,FMotorola reminds and recommends that
OL,10,Fconsumers use a PIN, password or
OL,11,Fpattern for enhanced security.
OL,13,F"Also, if a consumer chooses to use
OL,14,FFace Unlock for convenience after
OL,15,Fconsenting to use this feature, they
OL,16,Fwill also need to choose a pattern,
OL,17,FPIN or password to secure their device.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
