OL,3,C'Face unlock' feature can be tricked
OL,4,Cby photos on 60% of phones, tests show
OL,6,F"This added layer of protection
OL,7,Fsecures the phone if the consumer is
OL,8,Faway from their phone for more than
OL,9,Ffour hours or after restarting the
OL,10,Fdevice."
OL,12,FOnePlus added that it is transparent
OL,13,Fabout these risks, signalling to a
OL,14,Fmandatory "Statement on Using Face
OL,15,FRecognition" that every user must read
OL,16,Fbefore they can turn the feature on.
