OL,6,FThis notice tells owners that the
OL,7,Ftechnology is less secure than a
OL,8,Fnumeric password or fingerprint, and
OL,9,Fwarns that, in rare cases, the camera
OL,10,Fcould be tricked.
OL,12,FWhich? said that Nothing and Oppo did
OL,13,Fnot provide a comment. ITV News has
OL,14,Fapproached Asus, HMD, Nokia, Realme,
OL,15,FSamsung, Vivo, and Xiaomi for comment.
